== 爭議事件 ==
=== 2022年奧斯卡掌掴事件 ===
{{main|{{link-en|威爾·史密斯掌掴克里斯·洛克事件|Will Smith–Chris Rock slapping incident}}}}
在2022年3月27日的[[第94屆奧斯卡金像獎|第94屆奧斯卡金像獎]]上，頒獎人[[克里斯·洛克|克里斯·洛克]]在台上调侃威爾·史密斯的妻子[[潔達·蘋姬·史密斯|潔達·蘋姬·史密斯]]的光头，称其可以演出《[[魔鬼女大兵|魔鬼女大兵]]》续集。此笑话缘于他的妻子長期受[[脫髮|脫髮]]之苦，而決定留短髮或是剃髮，而被调侃电影中的女主角即为光头士兵形象。顾及妻子不满的史密斯憤而上台掌掴洛克，并在下台後两度以粗口警告“别再用你的臭嘴提起我老婆的名字”（{{lang|en|Keep my wife's name out your fucking mouth!}}），使場面一度尷尬，[[泰勒·派瑞|泰勒·派瑞]]和[[丹泽尔·华盛顿|丹泽尔·华盛顿]]等好友随即在台下安慰史密斯<ref>{{Cite web|title=奥斯卡尴尬一幕：威尔·史密斯不满妻子被调侃上台打人|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/culture/20220328/will-smith-chris-rock-oscars/|access-date=2022-03-28|date=2022-03-28|last=Stevens|first=Matt|work=纽约时报中文网|language=zh-hans|archive-date=2022-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220615121804/https://cn.nytimes.com/culture/20220328/will-smith-chris-rock-oscars/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Will Smith slaps Chris Rock at the Oscars over joke about Jada Pinkett Smith |url=https://www.nbcnews.com/pop-culture/pop-culture-news/will-smith-appears-hit-chris-rock-joke-wife-rcna21775 |website=NBC News |accessdate=2022-03-29 |date=2022-03-28 |first=Daniel |last=Arkin |archive-date=2022-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220329075609/https://www.nbcnews.com/pop-culture/pop-culture-news/will-smith-appears-hit-chris-rock-joke-wife-rcna21775 }}</ref>，洛克则以一句“这是电视史上最伟大一夜”（{{lang|en|That was a... greatest night in the history of television.}}）来为此圆场<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=myjEoDypUD8 |title=Watch the uncensored moment Will Smith smacks Chris Rock on stage at the Oscars, drops F-bomb |author=The Guardian |via=YouTube |access-date=2022-03-29 |archive-date=2022-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220329060337/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=myjEoDypUD8}}</ref>。此事件导致节目被停播約1分鐘。<ref>{{cite news |title=奧斯卡／頒獎人大開老婆玩笑 威爾史密斯怒了上台揍人 |url=https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A5%A7%E6%96%AF%E5%8D%A1-%E9%A0%92%E7%8D%8E%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E9%96%8B%E8%80%81%E5%A9%86%E7%8E%A9%E7%AC%91-%E5%A8%81%E7%88%BE%E5%8F%B2%E5%AF%86%E6%96%AF%E6%80%92%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%8A%E5%8F%B0%E6%8F%8D%E4%BA%BA-025754250.html |accessdate=2022-03-29 |archive-date=2022-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220525213152/https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A5%A7%E6%96%AF%E5%8D%A1-%E9%A0%92%E7%8D%8E%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E9%96%8B%E8%80%81%E5%A9%86%E7%8E%A9%E7%AC%91-%E5%A8%81%E7%88%BE%E5%8F%B2%E5%AF%86%E6%96%AF%E6%80%92%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%8A%E5%8F%B0%E6%8F%8D%E4%BA%BA-025754250.html }}</ref>

威尔·史密斯之后憑藉《王者理查》獲得最佳男主角，在上台领奖时泪流满面地向学院和其他提名者公开道歉，惟没有提及洛克。史密斯接下來在台上發表獲獎感言時落泪表示，他在《王者理查》剧中的角色是一名会为了保护家人而战的人，而爱会让人做出很多疯狂的事。而史密斯也特别援引[[丹泽尔·华盛顿|丹泽尔·华盛顿]]对他说的一句话：「到达人生的最高点，必须要小心，因为正是恶魔找上你的时候」<ref>{{Cite web|title=Denzel Washington Consoled Will Smith After He Lashed Out At Chris Rock|url=https://www.ladbible.com/entertainment/tv-and-film-denzel-washington-consoled-will-smith-after-he-confronted-chris-rock-20220328|access-date=2022-03-28|work=www.ladbible.com|language=en|archive-date=2022-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220419180856/https://www.ladbible.com/entertainment/tv-and-film-denzel-washington-consoled-will-smith-after-he-confronted-chris-rock-20220328}}</ref>。而根據斯科特·范伯格（{{lang|en|Scott Feinberg}}）在推特上上传的影片显示，史密斯的演讲让华盛顿泪流满面，两人更在演讲后互相拥抱，围绕奥斯卡颁奖典礼的紧张气氛才有所缓和。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Denzel Washington's Role In Calming Down Will Smith After Shocking Chris Rock Punch|url=https://clutchpoints.com/oscars-news-denzel-washingtons-role-in-calming-down-will-smith-after-shocking-chris-rock-punch/|access-date=2022-03-28|date=2022-03-28|last=Munar|first=Julio Luis|work=ClutchPoints|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220523173715/https://clutchpoints.com/oscars-news-denzel-washingtons-role-in-calming-down-will-smith-after-shocking-chris-rock-punch/}}</ref>

事件过后，洛克表示不考虑起诉史密斯<ref>{{Cite web |last=Yeo |first=Amanda |date=2022-03-28 |title=Chris Rock won't press charges against Will Smith for that Oscars slap |url=https://mashable.com/article/chris-rock-will-smith-oscars-charges |access-date=2022-03-28 |website=[[Mashable|Mashable]] |language=en |archive-date=2022-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220329075610/https://mashable.com/article/chris-rock-will-smith-oscars-charges}}</ref>，主办方[[美國影藝學院|美國影藝學院]]则对此事表示谴责，不容许任何形式的暴力行为<ref>{{Cite tweet |author-link=The Academy |user=TheAcademy |number=1508310547564953606 |date=2022-03-28 |title=The Academy does not condone violence of any form. Tonight we are delighted to celebrate our 94th Academy Awards winners, who deserve this moment of recognition from their peers and movie lovers around the world. |access-date=2022-03-29 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220328052902/https://twitter.com/TheAcademy/status/1508310547564953606 |archive-date=2022-03-28 |language=en-US}}</ref>，并宣布推进调查，根据学会章程、行为规范以及加州法律采取进一步措施，其包括可能中止史密斯的会员资格、逐出学会或者收回奖项<ref>{{Cite web |last=Puente |first=Maria |title=Academy launches formal review after Will Smith slaps Chris Rock on the Oscars stage |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/entertainment/celebrities/2022/03/28/oscars-chris-rock-will-smith-police/7189129001/ |access-date=2022-03-28 |website=USA TODAY |language=en-US |archive-date=2022-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220328201059/https://www.usatoday.com/story/entertainment/celebrities/2022/03/28/oscars-chris-rock-will-smith-police/7189129001/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=Melas |first=Chloe |date=2022-03-28 |title=Academy 'condemns' actions of Will Smith at Oscars, starts 'formal review' of slapping incident |url=https://www.cnn.com/2022/03/28/entertainment/academy-members-discuss-will-smith-oscars-slap/index.html |access-date=2022-03-28 |website=CNN |language=en |archive-date=2022-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220329070841/https://www.cnn.com/2022/03/28/entertainment/academy-members-discuss-will-smith-oscars-slap/index.html |url-status=live }}</ref>。影视媒体工会组织[[SAG-AFTRA|SAG-AFTRA]]也对此发表类似的谴责声明，并表示已与主办方与电视台取得联系以确保此事件得到妥善处理，而对于待定的演员处分事宜则不予置评<ref>{{cite web |last1=Robb |first1=David |title=SAG-AFTRA Condemns Will Smith’s “Unacceptable” Oscar Slap On Chris Rock |url=https://deadline.com/2022/03/will-smith-slap-sag-aftra-response-1234989566/ |website=Deadline |access-date=2022-03-28 |archive-date=2022-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220328225124/https://deadline.com/2022/03/will-smith-slap-sag-aftra-response-1234989566/}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Brian |first1=Welk |title=SAG-AFTRA Denounces Will Smith’s ‘Unacceptable’ Assault on Chris Rock at Oscars, Hints at Disciplinary Action |url=https://www.yahoo.com/entertainment/sag-aftra-denounces-smith-unacceptable-224948908.html |website=www.yahoo.com |access-date=2022-03-28 |archive-date=2022-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220329075610/https://www.yahoo.com/entertainment/sag-aftra-denounces-smith-unacceptable-224948908.html}}</ref>。28日，史密斯在社交媒体发文向洛克以及各方正式致歉<ref>{{cite web |title=Will Smith Apologizes to Chris Rock for Oscars Slap: ‘I Was Out of Line and I Was Wrong’ |url=https://variety.com/2022/film/news/will-smith-apologizes-chris-rock-slap-oscars-statement-1235216526/ |website=Variety |accessdate=2022-03-29 |date=2022-03-28 |first=Ellise |last=Shafer |archive-date=2022-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220328235719/https://variety.com/2022/film/news/will-smith-apologizes-chris-rock-slap-oscars-statement-1235216526/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=乌元春 |author2=王思予 |title=威尔·史密斯发文就奥斯卡颁奖礼扇耳光向克里斯·洛克道歉：我错了，深感羞愧 |url=https://world.huanqiu.com/article/47NuqEbXGPQ |website=环球网 |accessdate=2022-03-29 |date=2022-03-29 |archive-date=2022-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220523194500/https://world.huanqiu.com/article/47NuqEbXGPQ }}</ref>，進而又在4月1日退回影藝學院的會員資格，影藝學院主席{{link-en|大衛·魯賓|David Rubin (casting director)}}接受其辭呈，但表明會繼續調查<ref>{{Cite web |title=Will Smith resigns from Academy after Oscars slap |url=https://news.yahoo.com/smith-resigns-academy-oscars-slap-013500762.html |access-date=2022-04-02 |website=news.yahoo.com |language=en-US |archive-date=2022-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220402022750/https://news.yahoo.com/smith-resigns-academy-oscars-slap-013500762.html }}</ref>。魯賓和執行長哈德遜（{{lang|en|Dawn Hudson}}）则於同月8日作出决定，即自当天起的十年内不准许史密斯親自或以线上方式參加任何學院活動或项目，包括但不限於奧斯卡金像獎（被提名获奖的资格则不受影响）。史密斯随后对这一决定表示接受与尊重。<ref>{{cite web |title=Actor Will Smith banned from attending Oscars for 10 years |url=https://www.cnn.com/2022/04/08/entertainment/will-smith-academy-sanctions-decision/index.html |website=CNN |date=2022-04-08 |accessdate=2022-04-09 |first1=Chloe |last1=Melas |first2=Lisa |last2=France |archive-date=2022-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220411082016/https://www.cnn.com/2022/04/08/entertainment/will-smith-academy-sanctions-decision/index.html }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/amov/202204090010.aspx|title=掌摑代價 威爾史密斯未來10年遭禁參加奧斯卡典禮|date=2022-04-09|publisher=|accessdate=2022-04-09|archive-date=2022-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220614061223/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/amov/202204090010.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>

